          <div class="field-item"><p>The bipartisan Commission issued&nbsp;<em>Our Common Purpose: Reinventing American Democracy for the 21st Century</em>&nbsp;to both strengthen institutions and bolster civil society. Work is underway to advance initiatives rooted in that report that will help make the nation emerge as a more resilient democracy by 2026, the nation’s 250th anniversary.</p>
</div>
