        <h3 class="node-title card-project__title">
            <a href="/project/challenge-mass-incarceration-america" rel="bookmark"><span class="project__title project__title--card">The Challenge of Mass Incarceration in America</span>
</a>
        </h3>
        <div class="project__teaser project__teaser--card field field-node--field-teaser field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p>This study examined the scope of mass incarceration, its political significance, and its social impacts, weighing the concerns about crime control, rehabilitation, and more fundamental issues of social justice.</p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>

