                                    </div>
        <h3 class="node-title article-teaser__title">
            <a href="/news/dan-balz-repairing-american" rel="bookmark"><span class='field-wrapper article__title article__title--teaser'>American democracy is cracking. These ideas could help repair it.</span></a>
        </h3>
        <div class="article-teaser__body">
            <div class="article__teaser article__teaser--teaser field field-node--field-teaser-plain field-name-field-teaser-plain field-type-string-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item">Washington Post chief correspondent and Academy member Dan Balz highlights ways ordinary citizens can address problems with the U.S. political system in an op-ed that includes recommendations from Our Common Purpose, including independent redistricting commissions, expanding the House, implementing ranked choice voting, and more.<br />
<br />
</div>
      </div>
</div>

        </div>
        <div class="article__source article__source--teaser field field-node--field-article-source field-name-field-article-source field-type-entity-reference field-label-inline clearfix">
      <div class="field-label">Source</div>
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item">Washington Post</div>
      </div>
</div>

    </div>

</article>
