        <h3 class="node-title article-teaser__title">
            <a href="/news/here-new-way-measure-and-compare-americans-economic-wellbeing" rel="bookmark"><span class='field-wrapper article__title article__title--teaser'>Here is a new way to measure — and compare — Americans’ economic wellbeing</span></a>
        </h3>
        <div class="article-teaser__body">
            <div class="article__teaser article__teaser--teaser field field-node--field-teaser-plain field-name-field-teaser-plain field-type-string-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item">The new national dashboard released by the Academy&#039;s Commission on Reimagining Our Economy, the CORE Score, is mined for data about Massachusetts in this piece by WGBH. The coverage also connects the wellbeing assessed in the CORE Score to recommendations in the Commission&#039;s final report. </div>
      </div>
</div>

        </div>
